<span id="freeTextContainer16055351977180747846">“intuition is always right in at least two important ways;<br/>It is always in response to something.<br/>it always has your best interest at heart” <br/>― Gavin De Becker, The Gift of Fear: Survival Signals That Protect Us from Violence<br/><br/><br/><br/>It is a great book and worth reading. Mr. De Becker teaches you about using your intuition to scope out dangerous situations.<br/><br/>I will not say this book SOLVES everything. I do not believe that to be true. But it will resonate and it is well worth reading and maybe reading again .</span>

